    <!-- Info Section -->
    <div style="background: #fff; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 8px; margin-top: 2rem;">
      <h2 style="margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #2c3e50;">How This Grid Works</h2>
      <ul style="margin-left: 2rem; color: #555;">
        <li><strong>Auto-fill:</strong> Grid automatically fills with columns based on available space</li>
        <li><strong>minmax(300px, 1fr):</strong> Each card is minimum 300px, maximum equal fraction of available space</li>
        <li><strong>Gap:</strong> 2rem spacing between cards</li>
        <li><strong>Responsive:</strong> Cards stack to 1 column on mobile (below 768px)</li>
        <li><strong>Hover effect:</strong> Cards lift up on hover for better interactivity</li>
        <li><strong>Flexible height:</strong> Cards adjust to content using flexbox</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #2c3e50;">Customization Ideas</h3>
      <ul style="margin-left: 2rem; color: #555;">
        <li>Change <code>minmax(300px, 1fr)</code> to adjust card size</li>
        <li>Use <code>grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr)</code> for fixed 3-column layout</li>
        <li>Add <code>card--horizontal</code> class for horizontal card variant</li>
        <li>Adjust gap size for tighter or looser spacing</li>
        <li>Modify aspect ratio in <code>padding-bottom</code> for different image proportions</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

